        <div class="medium-8 medium-pull-4 columns">
        <div class="panel">
        <h3>Welcome</h3>
<div class="text-justify">
  <p>Bridle Path Stables is a full service boarding stable which is located in the East Fork Region of Clermont County offering over 50 miles of trails in and around the East Fork State Park. BPS is designed to be an enjoyable and comfortable place for your children and your equine family. Not only do we offer boarding services and professional training, we offer private and group riding lessons to kids and adults in disciplines including English, Western, Trail or Jumping. We also accommodate children and adults with Special Needs that are looking to discover an equine experience. In addition to the trails, lessons and individual training, BPS offers Day Camps throughout the year, 4-H clubs, assistance in selling or acquiring your horse, horses for lease and even Birthday Parties. Our facilities include both an indoor and outdoor arena, indoor wash-stall, individual tack storage, viewing area, many pastures and thirty 10x12 matted stalls. BPS offers a comfortable and welcoming atmosphere and much more.</p>

<div class="row">
<div class="large-12 columns">
<div class="right">
<p>Mary Rapp Huddle<br />
Bridle Path Stables<br />
513-202 4BPS</p>
</div>
